nmbrs = []
len_n = []
n = 0
for n1, n2 in tqdm(zip(df_number.number.values, df_number.number.values[1:])): 
    if n2 - n1 == 1:
        n += 1
        nmbrs.append(n1)
        nmbrs.append(n2)
    else: 
        len_n.append(n)
        n = 0
len_n = np.array(len_n)
